'''克里斯多福·布萊克'''（{{lang-en|Christopher Black}}，{{bd|1950年|1月16日||}}）是[[加拿大|加拿大]]刑事律師。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Canadian lawyer wins legal battle over Rwanda charges|url=https://www.thestar.com/news/world/2014/02/16/canadian_lawyer_wins_legal_battle_over_rwanda_charges.html|accessdate=2021-01-11|date=2014-02-16|work=thestar.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126014307/https://www.thestar.com/news/world/2014/02/16/canadian_lawyer_wins_legal_battle_over_rwanda_charges.html}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite news|title=Milosevic 'is being railroaded'|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/milosevic-is-being-railroaded/article1032301/|accessdate=2021-01-11|date=2001-07-17|work=Globe and Mail|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Comment juger le génocide rwandais ?|url=https://laviedesidees.fr/Comment-juger-le-genocide-rwandais.html|accessdate=2021-01-11|author=|date=2008-12-17|publisher=La Vie des idées|language=fr|author1=Liora Israël|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128032636/https://laviedesidees.fr/Comment-juger-le-genocide-rwandais.html}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=A Biden Administration Will Be Dominated by More U.S. Aggression|url=https://www.strategic-culture.org/news/2020/11/23/biden-administration-will-be-dominated-by-more-us-aggression/|accessdate=2021-01-11|publisher=Strategic Culture Foundation|date=2020-11-23|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111020113/https://www.strategic-culture.org/news/2020/11/23/biden-administration-will-be-dominated-by-more-us-aggression/}}</ref>

== 生平 ==
布萊克在[[多倫多|多倫多]]從事律師工作。原本他加入了[[新民主黨_(加拿大)|新民主黨]]，但在1999年[[北約轟炸南斯拉夫|北約轟炸南斯拉夫]]後，讓他轉而加入[[加拿大共產黨|加拿大共產黨]]，因為「它是唯一反對[[北約|北約]]攻擊的政黨」<ref name=":0" />。

2001年，他加入了捍衛斯洛波丹·米洛塞維奇國際委員會<ref>{{Cite news|title=Lawyers 'unlikely' to meet Milosevic soon|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/1425492.stm|date=2001-07-06|accessdate=2021-01-11|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|archive-date=2016-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160316045437/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/1425492.stm}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Defenders emerge for Milosevic|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2001/jul/07/warcrimes.ianblack|accessdate=2021-01-11|date=2001-07-07|publisher=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112023155/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2001/jul/07/warcrimes.ianblack}}</ref>，並擔任[[塞爾維亞|塞爾維亞]]前總統[[斯洛波丹·米洛塞維奇|斯洛波丹·米洛塞維奇]]的首席法律顧問<ref name=":1" />。

布萊克還在[[卢旺达问题国际刑事法庭|卢旺达问题国际刑事法庭]]當中為[[盧安達|盧安達]]前憲兵領袖{{le|奧古斯汀·恩丁迪利伊馬納|Augustin Ndindiliyimana}}辯護。2014年，恩丁迪利伊馬納被判無罪釋放<ref name=":0" />。

